title: S3 EP6: There Might Be Blood with Kirsten Nelson
description:
This week Maggie & Tim are joined by everyone's favorite Chief, Kirsten Nelson, to talk about Season Three Episode Six There Might Be Blood. The one where a death on an offshore oil rig leads to a jurisdictional battle between Chief Vick and her sister!
